  "detailed_description": "Pedro Temple is an action arcade platformer.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhen an ancient temple surfaces on the desert horizon, Pedro and co. set out to investigate.<br />\r\nPlayers will face waves of enemies in the temple's halls.<br />\r\nAfraid to go alone? Grab some friends and conquer the temple together!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you're feeling competitive, go against your friends in the gem-grabbing battle mode! Pick from four unique battle stages, and smack around your opponents while collecting gems!",
